highlights.text: “Cicak” by Cikgu Naim is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Malaysia at #1.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Malaysia the longest, at 150 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Malaysia. “Golden” is the highest at #24.
“Aku Negaraku” by AMP, Hafiz Suip, and Jaclyn Victor is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Malaysia, up 21 spots at #31.
